title: The Mad Hatters #38 Patreon Sneak Preview: Skankapolooza 2018
description: Thanks for tuning in for another excellent episode of the Secret Society of The Mad Hatters. This episode Sam and Ryan talk about their time at the 2018 Skankfest in New York City.  Thank you for your support.
